name: Web Momentum
overview:
Web Momentum, a newly established web development company, officially launches its website http://www.web-momentum.com giving businesses a high web momentum. With years of experience in high profile web development companies, we have gained enough expertise to cater global clients independently with a well defined set of process.

The core expertise of Web Momentum lies in Open Source Development which includes CMS and E-Commerce Development and ASP.NET Development. Web Momentum has been working since years on Open Source CMSs (Joomla, Word Press etc.) and E-Commerce (OS-Commerce, CRE-Loaded) and have gained an edge over other companies. Being based in India, we have an added advantage of cost effectiveness over other internal companies and providing an opportunity of outsourcing with quality work.

The technological expertise of Web Momentum include LAMP Environment (Linux, Apache, MYSQL, PHP) and ASP.NET. We have been serving worldwide clients successfully with quality delivery.
